name: Deep Sea (EhMeal)
description:
Float along little bubble, and learn from those around you. Listen to stories and swim as deep as you can, until you find what you're looking for.

. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .

Deep Sea is a narrative-focused game developed for UCSC's CMPM 80K Winter 2020 course. This game was made using Bitsy.

Development Team: Emil Saechao, Xiao Qing Yu
